# tune-play style guide

Follow `docs/style.mdc` in this repository. Summary:

- US English, serial comma, bullet lists end no stop unless sentence count >1
- No em dashes, no `---` markdown separators
- Use heading levels for structure, rare bolding, no **{bolded item}**: pattern lists
